com.bigdata.ha.msg

Interface IHARemoteRebuildRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IHAMessage, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HARemoteRebuildRequest

    public interface IHARemoteRebuildRequest
extends IHAMessage
    Message requesting disaster recovery of the service from the quorum leader. This message is sent to the service that must be recovered. The service will then message the leader to send its backing state.
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
